Pure Energy Corporation www.pure-energy.com The Pure Energy Corporation's P-series fuel is a blend of natural gas liquids, ethanol, and other biomassderived chemicals that are substantially renewable and domestically produced.
It has been designed to operate in flexible-fuel vehicles and can be mixed with gasoline.
The ozone-forming potential of the emissions is boasted to be 50% lower than reformulated gasoline.
For more information visit the "About Our Fuels" and "FAQs" sections of the site.
